data.description:
Beautiful updated home on 0.7 Acres in the Village of Sand Lake close to Public Lake Access! Home features main floor laundry, primary bedroom with his and her closets, kitchen with lots of storage, stainless steel appliances and a large open living room. Upper floor features four bedrooms.  Come outside to find a spacious fenced in back yard. Enjoy the comforts of home close to relaxation! Join us for open houses on Saturday 2/10/24 from 2-4PM and Sunday 2/11/24 from 1-3PM!

Schedule your showing today!
